#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:21
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A singleton that deals with inputs. This includes key presses, mouse "
"buttons and movement, joypads, and input actions. Actions and their "
"events can be set in the **Input Map** tab in the **Project > Project "
"Settings**, or with the :ref:`InputMap <class_InputMap>` class."
msgstr ""
"处理输入的单例。这包括按键、鼠标按钮和移动、操纵杆、以及输入操作。动作及其事件可以在 **项目>项目设置（Project > Project "
"Settings）** 的 **输入影射（Input Map）** 选项卡中设置，也可以使用 :ref:`InputMap "
"<class_InputMap>` 类进行设置。"

