#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:123
msgid "Enumerations"
msgstr "枚举"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:135
msgid "enum **MouseMode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **MouseMode**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:137
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_MODE_VISIBLE** = **0** --- Makes the mouse cursor visible if it "
"is hidden."
msgstr "**MOUSE_MODE_VISIBLE** = **0** —— 如果鼠标光标处于隐藏状态，则使其可见。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:139
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_MODE_HIDDEN** = **1** --- Makes the mouse cursor hidden if it is "
"visible."
msgstr "**MOUSE_MODE_HIDDEN** = **1** —— 如果可见，将鼠标光标隐藏。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:141
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_MODE_CAPTURED** = **2** --- Captures the mouse. The mouse will be"
" hidden and unable to leave the game window, but it will still register "
"movement and mouse button presses. On Windows and Linux, the mouse will "
"use raw input mode, which means the reported movement will be unaffected "
"by the OS' mouse acceleration settings."
msgstr ""
"**MOUSE_MODE_CAPTURED** = **2** —— "
"捕获鼠标。鼠标将被隐藏并且无法离开游戏窗口，但仍会注册移动和按下鼠标按钮。在Windows和Linux上，鼠标将使用原始输入模式，这意味着报告的移动，将不受操作系统的鼠标加速设置的影响。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:143
msgid ""
"**MOUSE_MODE_CONFINED** = **3** --- Makes the mouse cursor visible but "
"confines it to the game window."
msgstr "**MOUSE_MODE_CONFINED** = **3** —— 使鼠标光标可见，但将其限制在游戏窗口中。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:183
msgid "enum **CursorShape**:"
msgstr "枚举 **CursorShape**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:185
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_ARROW** = **0** --- Arrow cursor. Standard, default pointing "
"cursor."
msgstr "**CURSOR_ARROW** = **0** —— 箭头光标。标准的默认指针光标。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:187
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_IBEAM** = **1** --- I-beam cursor. Usually used to show where "
"the text cursor will appear when the mouse is clicked."
msgstr "**CURSOR_IBEAM** = **1** —— I字形光标。通常用于显示点击鼠标时，文本光标出现的位置。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:189
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_POINTING_HAND** = **2** --- Pointing hand cursor. Usually used "
"to indicate the pointer is over a link or other interactable item."
msgstr "**CURSOR_POINTING_HAND** = **2** —— 指向手形光标。通常用于指示在链接或其他可交互项上的指针。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:191
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_CROSS** = **3** --- Cross cursor. Typically appears over regions"
" in which a drawing operation can be performed or for selections."
msgstr "**CURSOR_CROSS** = **3** —— 十字光标。通常出现在可以执行绘制操作或进行选择的区域上方。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:193
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_WAIT** = **4** --- Wait cursor. Indicates that the application "
"is busy performing an operation. This cursor shape denotes that the "
"application is still usable during the operation."
msgstr "**CURSOR_WAIT** = **4** —— 等待光标。指示应用程序正忙于执行操作。此光标形状，表示该应用程序在操作过程中仍然可用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:195
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_BUSY** = **5** --- Busy cursor. Indicates that the application "
"is busy performing an operation. This cursor shape denotes that the "
"application isn't usable during the operation (e.g. something is blocking"
" its main thread)."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_BUSY** = **5** —— "
"繁忙光标。指示应用程序正忙于执行操作。此光标形状表示，该应用程序在操作期间无法使用（例如，某些内容阻塞了其主线程）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:197
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_DRAG** = **6** --- Drag cursor. Usually displayed when dragging "
"something."
msgstr "**CURSOR_DRAG** = **6** —— 拖动光标。通常在拖动时显示。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:199
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_CAN_DROP** = **7** --- Can drop cursor. Usually displayed when "
"dragging something to indicate that it can be dropped at the current "
"position."
msgstr "**CURSOR_CAN_DROP** = **7** —— 可以放下光标。通常在拖动某些东西时显示，表明可以将其放置在当前位置。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:201
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_FORBIDDEN** = **8** --- Forbidden cursor. Indicates that the "
"current action is forbidden (for example, when dragging something) or "
"that the control at a position is disabled."
msgstr "**CURSOR_FORBIDDEN** = **8** —— 禁止光标。指示当前操作是禁止的（例如，拖动某些东西时），或某个位置的控件被禁用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:203
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_VSIZE** = **9** --- Vertical resize mouse cursor. A double-"
"headed vertical arrow. It tells the user they can resize the window or "
"the panel vertically."
msgstr "**CURSOR_VSIZE** = **9** —— 垂直调整鼠标光标。双向垂直箭头。它告诉用户他们可以垂直调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:205
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_HSIZE** = **10** --- Horizontal resize mouse cursor. A double-"
"headed horizontal arrow. It tells the user they can resize the window or "
"the panel horizontally."
msgstr "**CURSOR_HSIZE** = **10** —— 水平调整鼠标光标。双向水平箭头。它告诉用户他们可以水平调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:207
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE** = **11** --- Window resize mouse cursor. The cursor "
"is a double-headed arrow that goes from the bottom left to the top right."
" It tells the user they can resize the window or the panel both "
"horizontally and vertically."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE** = **11** —— "
"窗口调整鼠标光标。光标是从左下角到右上角的双向箭头。它告诉用户他们可以水平和垂直调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:209
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_FDIAGSIZE** = **12** --- Window resize mouse cursor. The cursor "
"is a double-headed arrow that goes from the top left to the bottom right,"
" the opposite of :ref:`CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE "
"<class_Input_constant_CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE>`. It tells the user they can "
"resize the window or the panel both horizontally and vertically."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_FDIAGSIZE** = **12** —— 窗口调整鼠标光标。光标是一个双向箭头，从左上角到右下角，与 "
":ref:`CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE <class_Input_constant_CURSOR_BDIAGSIZE>` "
"相对。它告诉用户他们可以水平和垂直调整窗口或面板的大小。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:211
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_MOVE** = **13** --- Move cursor. Indicates that something can be"
" moved."
msgstr "**CURSOR_MOVE** = **13** —— 移动光标。表示可以移动某些东西。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:213
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_VSPLIT** = **14** --- Vertical split mouse cursor. On Windows, "
"it's the same as :ref:`CURSOR_VSIZE <class_Input_constant_CURSOR_VSIZE>`."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_VSPLIT** = **14** —— 垂直拆分鼠标光标。在Windows上，它与 :ref:`CURSOR_VSIZE "
"<class_Input_constant_CURSOR_VSIZE>` 相同。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:215
msgid ""
"**CURSOR_HSPLIT** = **15** --- Horizontal split mouse cursor. On Windows,"
" it's the same as :ref:`CURSOR_HSIZE "
"<class_Input_constant_CURSOR_HSIZE>`."
msgstr ""
"**CURSOR_HSPLIT** = **15** —— 水平拆分鼠标光标。在Windows上，它与 :ref:`CURSOR_HSIZE "
"<class_Input_constant_CURSOR_HSIZE>` 相同。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_input.rst:217
msgid "**CURSOR_HELP** = **16** --- Help cursor. Usually a question mark."
msgstr "**CURSOR_HELP** = **16** —— 帮助光标。通常是一个问号。"

